Subject: How Not To Draw Comics
Description: This is a judgment free zone...but have you ever looked at a comic and thought, 'Wow that doesn't look right'. You've come to the right place. We'll study the comic greats and have a laugh as we explore the made up muscle groups, humanly impossible poses, and just downright ponder how it made it from the drawing table to the rack at your local comic book store!  Speakers include:Galen Nelson, BluRaven C. Houvener, Jon David - Track: Comics  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Influence of Anime in Media
Description: Fans of anime and manga know it's influenced our lives, but what about the other kinds of media we consume? Television, music, and games draw more and more inspiration from anime every day, and not always in obvious ways.  Speakers include:Christina June, Galen Nelson - Track: Anime  - Duration: 50 minutes
